            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Aelia Asteria Aelio Anti<lb break="no" n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">o</supplied>chiano tesserario <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>XI <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audiae</ex></expan> dulcissimo quando <note>sic</note> <lb n="4"/>marito suo instruxit mo<lb break="no" n="5"/>nimentum et statuam <lb n="6"/>et a<supplied reason="lost">r</supplied><expan><abbr>ulam</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> cum subposi<lb break="no" n="7"/>to in terram sarcophago <lb n="8"/>lapideo secundum volun<lb break="no" n="9"/>tatem <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>upra</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>cripti</ex></expan> Antiochiani me<lb break="no" n="10"/>moriae causa huius exem<lb break="no" n="11"/>plaria in sf<expan><ex>r</ex><abbr>ag</abbr></expan><supplied reason="lost">id</supplied>is <note>sic</note> ceris duobus re<lb break="no" n="12"/>posita sunt in archia publi<lb break="no" n="13"/>ca Cibyratorum </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Αἰλία Ἀστερία Αἰλίῳ Ἀντι<lb break="no" n="2"/>οχιανῷ, τεσσεραρίῳ λεγ(ιῶνος) <lb n="3"/>ιαʹ Κλ(αυδίας), τῷ γλυκυτάτῳ γε<lb break="no" n="4"/>νομένῳ ἀνδρὶ αὐτῆς <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">κα</supplied>τ<supplied reason="lost">εσ</supplied>κεύασε τὸ μνημεῖ<lb break="no" n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">ο</supplied>ν καὶ τὸν ἀνδριάντα σὺν <lb n="7"/>τῇ βάσει κ<supplied reason="lost">α</supplied>ὶ τῇ ὑποκει<lb break="no" n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">μ</supplied>ένῃ ὑπὸ <supplied reason="lost">γῇ σ</supplied>ορῷ, καθὼς <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">α</supplied>ὐτὸς διετάξατο, μνείας <lb n="10"/>χάριν· τούτου ἀντίγραφα <lb n="11"/>δύο εἰς τὰ ἀρχεῖα ἀπετέθη.
            </ab></div></div>
